{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/create-react-app-settings/","webpackCompilationHash":"4c48fe7af45f72ccf1ce","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"420875a9-7b50-5b04-a305-17a6fe4ab7b4","html":"<figure>\n    <img src=\"/media/20190810-photo1.jpeg\" alt=\"unsplash-film\">\n    <!-- <figcaption>Splendid</figcaption> -->\n</figure>\n<h3 id=\"enter-following-commands-line-in-terminal\"><a href=\"#enter-following-commands-line-in-terminal\" aria-label=\"enter following commands line in terminal permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enter following commands line in Terminal</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn global add npx\nnpm i npx -g\nnpx create-react-app koflix  //&gt;&gt;koflix is my folder name. Create your own file.\n\ncd koflix\n\ncode .   // open VS Code Editor</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"if-you-have-issues-installing-npx-take-a-look-at-here\"><a href=\"#if-you-have-issues-installing-npx-take-a-look-at-here\" aria-label=\"if you have issues installing npx take a look at here permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>If you have issues installing npx, take a look at <a href=\"https://www.notion.so/bpratings/JS-Unable-to-install-npx-eae73dc6edab485c843d789ff519494a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here.</a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-delete-unnecessary-files\"><a href=\"#1-delete-unnecessary-files\" aria-label=\"1 delete unnecessary files permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Delete unnecessary files</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">src/App.js</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">src/App.css</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">src/index.css</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">src/App.test.js</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">src/logo.svg</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-prepare-for-basic-settings-of-components-files-by-removing-unnecessary-stuff-in-appjs-and-indexjs\"><a href=\"#2-prepare-for-basic-settings-of-components-files-by-removing-unnecessary-stuff-in-appjs-and-indexjs\" aria-label=\"2 prepare for basic settings of components files by removing unnecessary stuff in appjs and indexjs permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Prepare for basic settings of <strong>Components</strong> files by removing unnecessary stuff in “App.js” and “index.js”.</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">//index.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> App <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>App <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-create-a-new-file-calledenv-next-to-gitignore-and-add-node_pathsrc-inside-env-folder-env-helps-srcsource-folder-to-look-at-files-separated-between-folders-later-youre-going-to-create-a-new-components-file-inside-src-and-put-indexjs-so-that-you-can-handle-all-the-components-with-ease\"><a href=\"#3-create-a-new-file-calledenv-next-to-gitignore-and-add-node_pathsrc-inside-env-folder-env-helps-srcsource-folder-to-look-at-files-separated-between-folders-later-youre-going-to-create-a-new-components-file-inside-src-and-put-indexjs-so-that-you-can-handle-all-the-components-with-ease\" aria-label=\"3 create a new file calledenv next to gitignore and add node_pathsrc inside env folder env helps srcsource folder to look at files separated between folders later youre going to create a new components file inside src and put indexjs so that you can handle all the components with ease permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Create a new file called<code class=\"language-text\">.env</code> next to <code class=\"language-text\">.gitignore</code> and add <code class=\"language-text\">NODE_PATH=src</code> inside <code class=\"language-text\">.env</code> folder. .env helps src(source folder) to look at files separated between folders. Later, you’re going to create a new <code class=\"language-text\">Components</code> file inside <code class=\"language-text\">src</code> and put <code class=\"language-text\">index.js</code> so that you can handle all the components with ease.</h3>\n<p>Don’t forget to add prop-types in Terminal.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add prop-types</code></p>\n<p>Once installed, let’s begin.</p>\n<h2 id=\"yarn-start\"><a href=\"#yarn-start\" aria-label=\"yarn start permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">yarn start</code></h2>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>We are creating wealth every time we write a code</strong></p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/create-react-app-settings/","tagSlugs":["/tag/react/","/tag/create-react-app/","/tag/npx/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-08-10T18:25:42.199Z","description":"npx create-react-app <your foldername>","tags":["React","create-react-app","npx"],"title":"[React] Create-react-app-settings"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/create-react-app-settings/"}}}